org.blockchain_innovation.factom.client.api.rpc

Class RpcRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchain_innovation.factom.client.api.rpc.RpcRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RpcRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Factom APIs use JSON-RPC, which is a remote procedure call protocol encoded in JSON. This RPC request object represents the the request of a API call to the factomd or walletd node
    See Also:
